name: GeoGebraHtml
body:
###Documentation
* `Position` - generic `x;y` object
* * `Slope` - different implementation of `Position`
* `Container` - holds `Element`s
* `Element` - generic geometric object
* * `Point` - describes one point on 2D plane; two points with same position might exist
* * `Line` - determined by either two `Point`s or a `Point` and `Slope`
* * `Circle` - determined by either two `Point`s or a `Point` and radius
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
